name: 20211217_Strangeness_b aka Braque
description:
My wife, like most us, loves flowers a lot. Instead of being a boring landscape painter most of the time, why don't I spend some time to draw some flowers to her? So I opened her beloved book of flowers and came over a flower picture from Braque. Voila, the Braque I haven't seen before. I chose some flowers from his picture and recreated this. Hope my wife may love it. 
And hope you, the stranger, will also like this gift too.
